reviews.review_text:
What would your Mamma think? As much as i enjoyed 10/16/89-NJ
this is a rough next show.
I wrote like 3 pages of comments 
and thankfully hit delete by accident.
Band sounds extremely out of synch
for a majority of the evening.

Brent has his moments (exploring being a front man)
Good- Peggy O, Ship of Fools, 
Better-Gimme Some & Watchtower, Good Lovin'

(3 stars probably generous )
but they do sound tighter , leaner coming out of space..
